(13, '[{\"pl\":\"usiłować, starać się, dążyć (do czegoś)\",\"en\":\"strive\",\"example\":\"it can help us learning about who we are and this can enable us to strive to be better people in the future.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"walczyć przeciw czemuś, zmagać się z czymś\",\"en\":\"strive (strove, stroven)\",\"example\":\"Stop striving against your fate.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"kończyć się something\",\"en\":\"result in\",\"example\":\"When people see a composed and self-assured individual, they are likely to be affected in a positive way. They too may adopt you good feeling and this can result in a more optimistic, constructive relationship.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"dopasowywać, dostosowywać\",\"en\":\"tailor\",\"example\":\"We need to tailor our approach to individual situations.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"kolejny\",\"en\":\"consecutive\",\"example\":\"You cannot be on the list of worst employee of the month for six consecutive months and then suddenly have ideas and expect your boss take it serious.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"propozycja, oświadczyny\",\"en\":\"proposal\",\"example\":\"She accepted his proposal \\/ She was pleased and accepted my proposal\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"bezpośrednia trasa\",\"en\":\"direct route\",\"example\":\"You know, It can be the direct route to her heart.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"powiększyć się, rozwinąć się \\/ rozluźnić się\",\"en\":\"expand\",\"example\":\"We can experience an absolute shift (absolutnej zmiany) in our emotional range, when our horizons expand through new languages.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"otwarty (na pomysły, sugestie), chłonny, receptywny (umysł)\",\"en\":\"receptive\",\"example\":\"It strenghtens your mind and makes you receptive to others.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"ciągle, bez przerwy\",\"en\":\"continouously\",\"example\":\"She has been wearing it continuously since Monday morning.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"płaszczyzna porozumienia, wspólna płaszczyzna\",\"en\":\"common ground\",\"example\":\"It shows a kind of respect and common ground, allowing a connection that runs much deeper than the surface.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"wgląd, wyobrażenie,\",\"en\":\"insight\",\"example\":\"That may give us some insight into their methods.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"nie mający sobie równych,\",\"en\":\"second to none\",\"example\":\"This asset is second to 