\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"nieudolny, niewydajny, nieskuteczny\",\"en\":\"inefficient\",\"example\":\"This training will be inefficient if you don\'t prepare a good programme.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"czerpać z czegoś garściami, wykorzystać coś w pełni\",\"en\":\"make the most of something\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"poddawać się czemuś, ulegać pokusie\",\"en\":\"succumb\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"poddawanie się czemuś, uleganie pokusie\",\"en\":\"succumbing\",\"example\":\"They get stressed out by their intense quest to find what they love and end up giving up their search, succumbing to a life they don\'t really love.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"głęboki, intensywny \\/ reagujący emocjonalnie\",\"en\":\"intense\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"poszukiwanie, dążenie\",\"en\":\"quest\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"wrodzone\",\"en\":\"innate\",\"example\":\"The ability of quick reading is my innate strenght. My innate streght is a ability of quick reading.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"szok, zaskoczenie\",\"en\":\"eye-opener\",\"example\":\"These tests can be eye-opening\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"klarowność, czystość, jasność\",\"en\":\"clarity\",\"example\":\"Clarity comes from taking action.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"uzdolnienie, zdolność\",\"en\":\"aptitude\",\"example\":\"Ultimately, no matter how many aptitude tests you take, you won\'t know what you trully love until you can try it\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"ochota, pragnienie \\/ verb: życzyć sobie, pragnąć, pożądać\",\"en\":\"desire\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"uraza, irytacja\",\"en\":\"pique\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"obrażać, urazić \\/ wzbudzić (zainteresowanie, ciekawość)\",\"en\":\"pique\",\"example\":\"Pay attention to what tugs at your heart and captures your attention, and take action related to the topics that pique your interest.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":\"Mateusz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Pankowski\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/14\\/main_14604690973859.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"powiązane z czymś\",\"en\":\"related to something\",\"example\":\"I\'m looking for information related to politics. \\/ Both problems are related.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":14,\"imie\":