(25, '[{\"pl\":\"When something unfortunate happens, it can be called a \\\"tough break\\\".\",\"en\":\"a tough break\",\"example\":\"It was a tough break for us when Caroline quit. She was one of our top performers.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To be \\\"ahead of the curve\\\" means to be more advanced than the competition.\",\"en\":\"ahead of the curve\",\"example\":\"We\'re investing a lot of money in research and development so we can stay ahead of the curve.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"\\\"ASAP\\\" is an acronym for \\\"as soon as possible.\\\"\",\"en\":\"ASAP\",\"example\":\"I need to finish these reports. My boss needs them ASAP.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"At stake\\\" means at risk.\",\"en\":\"at stake\",\"example\":\"I\'m a little nervous about giving this presentation. There\'s a lot at stake.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To go \\\"back to square one\\\" means to start something over again.\",\"en\":\"back to square one\",\"example\":\"Our programmers identified what they thought the problem was with the software. After working for several hours, it turns out that the problem is something different. We\'re back to square one, unfortunately.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To go \\\"back to the drawing board\\\" means to start something over and go back to the planning stage.\",\"en\":\"back to the drawing board\",\"example\":\"The prototype wasn\'t successful. We have to go back to the drawing board.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A \\\"backroom deal\\\" is an agreement or decision that is made without the public knowing about it.\",\"en\":\"backroom deal\",\"example\":\"I think they got the government contract because of a backroom deal.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A \\\"ballpark number\\\" is a very inexact estimate.\",\"en\":\"ballpark number\\/\",\"example\":\"I\'m not sure what a Super Bowl commercial costs, but to give you a ballpark figure I\'d say about three million dollars.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"What happens in secret or not in front of the general public is said to happen \\\"behind the scenes.\\\"\",\"en\":\"behind the scenes\",\"example\":\"They make it look so effortless, but they do a lot of hard work and planning behind the scenes.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Everything that is involved with a particular situation is called \\\"the big picture.\\\"\",\"en\":\"big picture\",\"example\":\"Even though we all have very specific tasks to do, our manager makes sure we don\'t lose sight of the big picture.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A \\\"blue collar worker\\\" is someone who works with his hands (manufacturing, construction, maintenance, etc.).\",\"en\":\"blue collar\",\"example\":\"It\'s a blue collar town with a lot of farmers and factory workers.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A white collar worker is someone who works in an office (customer service, management, sales, etc.).\",\"en\":\"white collar\",\"example\":\"There  are 2000 white collars in this office.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To do things \\\"by the book\\\" means to do things according to company policy or the law. It means to follow the rules 100%.\",\"en\":\"by the book\",\"example\":\"We are regularly audited by several regulatory agencies. It\'s important that we do everything by the book\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To \\\"call it a day\\\" means to decide to stop working for the day.\",\"en\":\"call it a day\",\"example\":\"Well, John, it\'s 7:00 and I\'m getting hungry. How about we call it a day?\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"\\\"A change of pace\\\" is something different from a normal routine or schedule.\",\"en\":\"change of pace\",\"example\":\"\\\"A change of pace\\\" is something different from a normal routine or schedule.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To \\\"come up short\\\" means to try to achieve something but fail. We often say that someone has \\\"come up short\\\" when someone fails to achieve a goal, but not completely.\",\"en\":\"come up short\",\"example\":\"The charity fund raiser was supposed to raise three million dollars, but we came up short.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To do something \\\"behind someone\'s back\\\" means to do something without someone\'s knowledge and in an unfair way.\",\"en\":\"behind someone\'s back\",\"example\":\"She didn\'t think it would be fair to go behind his back and talk to management, so she confronted him directly.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To \\\"corner a market\\\" means to dominate a particular market.\",\"en\":\"corner a market\",\"example\":\"Apple has cornered the market on mp3 players. They have a large percentage of market share.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To \\\"cut corners\\\" means to take shortcuts and find an easier or cheaper way to do something.\",\"en\":\"cut corners\",\"example\":\"We don\'t cut corners on our luxury products.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To \\\"cut one\'s losses\\\" means to stop doing something that is unproductive and won\'t ever generate results.\",\"en\":\"cut one\'s losses\",\"example\":\"Our advertising campaign was expensive and not showing results, so we cut our losses.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"\\\"Cut-throat\\\" is used to describe something that is very intense, aggressive, and merciless.\",\"en\":\"cut-throat\",\"example\":\"In business school, the competition was cut-throat.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A \\\"diamond in the rough\\\" is something or someone that has a lot of potential but first requires a lot of work.\",\"en\":\"diamond in the rough\",\"example\":\"He was a diamond in the rough. He was intelligent and had great ideas, but his management and English skills weren\'t very good.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"\\\"Easy come, easy go,\\\" is an expression used to communicate that something gained easily is also lost easily. We often use this expression after something has been lost.\",\"en\":\"easy come, easy go\",\"example\":\"A lot of people who inherit money waste it on stupid things. I guess it\'s easy come, easy go.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"\\\"Fifty-fifty\\\" means something is divided equally -- 50% for one party, 50% for the other party.\",\"en\":\"fifty-fifty\",\"example\":\"My business partner and I split everything fifty-fifty.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"If you start a business, project, or something else from zero, you start it \\\"from the ground up.\\\"\",\"en\":\"from the ground up\",\"example\":\"Bill Gates built Microsoft from the ground up.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A \\\"game plan\\\" is a strategy or plan.\",\"en\":\"game plan\",\"example\":\"They\'re not sure what their game plan is for the upcoming election.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"}]', 'Business Idioms', 'The most common business idioms', 'B2', 4, 0, '2016-12-27 19:24:34', 1),
(26, '[{\"pl\":\"shortened form of a word or expression that uses the first few letters or the main letters of the word to represent it\",\"en\":\"abbreviation\",\"example\":\"The abbreviation \'RAM\' stands for Random Access Memory.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"critical study or examination of something\",\"en\":\"analysis\",\"example\":\"A financial analysis was carried out in order to improve cost efficiency.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"can be found or used etc.\",\"en\":\"available\",\"example\":\"Available memory refers to how much RAM is not being used by the computer.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"past history of a person\'s or company\'s life\",\"en\":\"background\",\"example\":\"It\'s always a good idea to research a company\'s background before doing business with them.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"official document awarded by standard setting organizations that indicates competency in a certain professional field\",\"en\":\"certification\",\"example\":\"Earning the latest Microsoft certifications may help you further your career.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"most important or main\",\"en\":\"chief\",\"example\":\"The Chief Information Officer (CIO) is responsible for the computer systems of a company.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/ma