(39, '[{\"pl\":\"a new established business (some people relate it only to innovative businesses)\",\"en\":\"start-up\",\"example\":\"San Francisco is the home for many star-ups.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"it will affect you strongly, it will  cause you great pleasure or surprise\",\"en\":\"it will blow you away\",\"example\":\"This new feature will blow you away\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"successful\",\"en\":\"ahead of the game\",\"example\":\"This business is ahead of the game\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"the strategy of reaching an objective\",\"en\":\"game plan\",\"example\":\"If we want to survive we have to introduce a better game plan.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"something that will probably not succeed but is worth trying\",\"en\":\"long shot\",\"example\":\"This move was definitely a long shot. It was very risky.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to lose something in return of gaining something\",\"en\":\"trade-off\",\"example\":\"There is a trade-off between doing the job accurately and doing it quickly.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"physical or mental exhaustion\",\"en\":\"burn out rate\",\"example\":\"In the banking sector the burn out rate is very high\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"miss the opportunity\",\"en\":\"miss the boat\",\"example\":\"He thinks we\'re missing the boat on improving relations with Russia.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to confront a problem head on\",\"en\":\"take the bull by the horns\",\"example\":\"to confront a problem head-on and deal with it openly.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to think differently from a new perspective\",\"en\":\"think out of the box\",\"example\":\"e need to think out of the box if we are going to come up with something really new.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"compromise\",\"en\":\"meeting someone halfway\",\"example\":\"They settled the argument by agreeing to meet each other halfway.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"a situation in which everyone participating come out on top; everyone wins or gets what they want\",\"en\":\"win-win situation\",\"example\":\"Even if you don\'t win your debate, you will come away from the experience better informed than when you started. It\'s a win-win situation.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"something that has happened and can’t be changed\",\"en\":\"water over the bridge\",\"example\":\"George and I were business partners once, but that\'s all water under the bridge now.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"better than average\",\"en\":\"ahead of the curve\",\"example\":\"I\'m not sure how I did on that Prince2 exam, but I think I\'ll end up ahead of the curve.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"not in debt; in a financially profitable condition.\",\"en\":\"In the black\",\"example\":\"I wish my accounts were in the black.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"experiencing the situation of spending more money than you earned.\",\"en\":\"in the red\",\"example\":\"The recent sales data have shown that the release of our newest game will be a failure. I am afraid, that we will be in the red this year.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"active and aware of things\",\"en\":\"on the ball\",\"example\":\"Their staff seems to be really on the ball, able to get projects done on time.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to locate the cause of (a problem) and remove or treat it\",\"en\":\"troubleshoot\",\"example\":\"The service it performed in trouble-shooting an employee problem\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to identify and rectify problems or minor defects in a system\",\"en\":\"get the bugs out\",\"example\":\"We must get all of the bugs out\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"move ahead and do well\",\"en\":\"take off\",\"example\":\"When your business begins to take off you should think about investments.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"have the same understanding or amount of knowledge.\",\"en\":\"on the same page\",\"example\":\"We’re not on the same page. Listen carefully to what I am telling you.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to agree with someone\",\"en\":\"see eye to eye\",\"example\":\"He\'s asked for a transfer because he doesn\'t see eye to eye with the new manager.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"doing something correctly or well; following the right set of assumptions.\",\"en\":\"on the right track\",\"example\":\"Tom is on the right track and will solve the system crash soon.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to mess up\",\"en\":\"screw up\",\"example\":\"This is the chef\'s screw-up, not mine.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to fail in some way\",\"en\":\"drop the ball\",\"example\":\"You can\'t trust John to do the job right. He\'s always dropping the ball.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to be always prepared for everything that might happen\",\"en\":\"stay on top of things\",\"example\":\"Stay on top of things – just slide open your Notifications panel\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"to have or do two good things at the same time that are impossible to have or do at the same time\",\"en\":\"you can’t have your cake and eat it, too\",\"example\":\"You can\'t have your cake and eat it - if you want more local services, you can\'t expect to pay less tax.\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"}]', 'Useful business idioms and expressions', 'for the IT-Business conversations', 'B2', 4, 3, '2017-05-07 20:12:58', 1);
