(54, '[{\"pl\":\"the particular group of people or businesses that an start-up is intended to reach\",\"en\":\"Target Market\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"a strategic marketing approach focused on creating and distributing valuable, relevant, and consistent content to attract and retain a clearly-defined audience\",\"en\":\"Content Marketing\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"a center where start-ups are “incubated” through mentorship, space and sometimes cash.\",\"en\":\"Accelerator (or  Incubator)\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A rich individual potentially interested in investing in your company.\",\"en\":\"Accredited Investor\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Paid content that is meant to look and feel like a real story or blog post.\",\"en\":\"Advertainment\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"An extremely pretentious way of saying on the vanguard since every person in start-ups thinks he or she is there.\",\"en\":\"Bleeding Edge\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Using “friends and family” cash to get going\",\"en\":\"Boot-Strapping\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Business to Business. Your company sells things to other companies.\",\"en\":\"B2B\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Business to Consumer. Your company sells stuff to the masses.\",\"en\":\"B2C\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"How fast you are blowing through your cash.\",\"en\":\"Burn Rate\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Customers lost subsequent to acquisition in a subscription-based business model.\",\"en\":\"Churn Rate\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Usually applies to vesting schedules (shares given to employees over time). Cliffs are a way for the CEO to fire employees or let them leave without giving them stock within a limited period of time\",\"en\":\"Cliff\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A nice business but not something massively scalable.\",\"en\":\"Cottage Business\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A 10-slide power point presentation that covers all aspects of your business in a concise and compelling way.\",\"en\":\"Pitch Deck\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Something that completely changes the way society does something (e.g. Uber\\/Lyft vs. Taxis or Amazon vs. in-store shopping).\",\"en\":\"Disruptive Technology\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"How you will sell the company and make your investors lots of money.  Who is going to buy you and why?\",\"en\":\"Exit Strategy\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Not every start-up is the first to market, but if you are, you want to point that out to investors.\",\"en\":\"First Mover Advantage\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"You give the basic product away for free and then try to upsell features to your customers.\",\"en\":\"Freemium\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Adding a game layer to a website or product experience that encourages people to use it with rewards of various kinds. People love games.\",\"en\":\"Gamify\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A term coined by Sean Ellis to describe a marketing technique that focuses on quickly finding scalable growth through non-traditional and inexpensive tactics such as the use of social media.\",\"en\":\"Growth Hacking\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"The shape of the growth curve VCs want to see and believe! This means your start-up will have to double sales every year.\",\"en\":\"Hockey Stick\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Intellectual Property. This can be a patent  or formula like Coke.\",\"en\":\"IP\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Code for try something, do it wrong, and try it again in a slightly different way with the hopes of achieving a better result.\",\"en\":\"Iterate\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"To start a company or push a website live.\",\"en\":\"Launch\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"The core mission of a lean start-up is to prove the business concept as quickly and cheaply as possible.\",\"en\":\"Lean Startup\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Use something (for example technology) to your advantage.\",\"en\":\"Leverage\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Selling something at a loss as a form of marketing expense to bring in customers you expect repeat business from.\",\"en\":\"Loss Leader Pricing\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"The easiest thing your company can do to bring cash in the door.\",\"en\":\"Low Hanging Fruit\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"How much of your potential market are you capturing and how quickly.\",\"en\":\"Market Penetration\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"How you are making money or how you plan to make it.\",\"en\":\"Monetize\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Minimum Viable Product. The very basic version of a product required to achieve proof that the concept works.\",\"en\":\"MVP\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Change directions as a company. This is usually used to describe going after a different market segment or using an established technology for an entirely new purpose.\",\"en\":\"Pivot\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Profitable enough to cover costs and basic living\\nexpenses for everyone working at a startup.\",\"en\":\"Ramen Profitable\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A site built for optimal viewing of a website across all devices (e.g. laptops, tablets, smartphones)\",\"en\":\"Responsive Design\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Return On Investment.\",\"en\":\"ROI\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"How long you have until the cash runs out and you must turn off the lights.\",\"en\":\"Runway\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Software As A Service. You sell subscriptions to use your software.\",\"en\":\"SaaS\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Something that can grow to a huge size because the market and demand is big enough or because you will be able to move into different markets with your product.\",\"en\":\"Scaleable  business\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Shares of your company given in exchange for work done.\",\"en\":\"Sweat Equity\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"The document that outlines what the Investors will get for what they put in — including % ownership and voting rights.\",\"en\":\"Term Sheet\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Proof that people are actually buying and using your stuff.\",\"en\":\"Traction\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"What your company is being valued at. “Pre-money valuation” is the value before you take investors’ cash. “Post-money valuation” is that amount plus the investment put in.\",\"en\":\"Valuation\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"The feature(s) or elements that make your business or product uniquely attractive to consumers.\",\"en\":\"Value Prop\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"A product you are selling but have not actually made (and may never make).  It is a way to test market demand. Some people think it is sleazy, but it is very common.\",\"en\":\"Vaporware\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Venture Capital or Venture Capitalist. They have cash, but you might not want it.\",\"en\":\"VC\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"},{\"pl\":\"Comparing two versions to see which performs better.\",\"en\":\"A\\/B Testing\",\"example\":\"\",\"image\":\"\",\"audio\":\"\",\"author\":4,\"imie\":\"Łukasz\",\"nazwisko\":\"Fabian\",\"avatar\":\"img\\/avatar\\/4\\/main_14550384428268.jpg\"}]', 'Startup', 'Startup Jargon Words You Need To Know', 'B2', 4, 3, '2017-05-25 17:04:42', 2);
